snippet.title: Blackrock Mountain Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Blackrock Mountain: A Hearthstone Adventure is coming soon! Face fearsome foes in Blackrock Mountain, Hearthstone’s next single player Adventure. Log in and test your wits against five fiery wings, each packed with iconic bosses. Earn powerful new cards for your Hearthstone decks! Visit www.blackrockmountain.com to learn more! 

Get started at
http://PlayHearthstone.com
